(94, 'SUB0093', 'Earth Science', 'earth-science', '', 'download26.jpg', '<p class=\"style4\" xss=removed><strong>Earth Science assignment help</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"style4\" xss=removed>Earth science is referred to study of the Earth and geographic evidence grouped under the solid earth science, known as ‘Geology’, derived from the Greek word geo which refers to ‘earth’ and logy which means ‘study of’. So geology is the study of Earth. Earth is an enormous system and several million years old as; however, the determination of Earth’s age has become difficult owing to the eradication of old rocks by natural ruin. <span xss=removed>Basically, the study of evolution of earth from its evolution till date is actually what the earth science is all about. The Earth Science subject helps people to understand how earth evolved and exactly what the changes are, that occurred within the earth. If we have a look at earth’s interior, we understand that beneath its crust is mantle, which gets heated by heavy elements or radioactive decay. This layer isn’t very solid and it consists of magma, which is there in the convection mode and it helps the lithospheric plate to move gradually. Hence, the base of earth keeps moving gradually, at times leading to earthquakes. The Earth is known to be an electromagnet. Since, inner core of Earth is soft iron, surrounded by the semi-liquid materials; this creates a great electromagnetic effect.</span> <span class=\"style12\"><span xss=removed>Now, coming to earth’s atmosphere, the earth has 5 layers namely troposphere, mesosphere, stratosphere, exosphere, and thermosphere. The troposphere is base level and it consists of argon, oxygen and nitrogen. All other layers comprises small amount of gas including water vapor and carbon dioxide that help in </span></span><strong><span xss=removed>green house effect</span></strong><span class=\"style12\"><span xss=removed>, and that is very vital in sustaining human life on earth</span></span><span xss=removed>.</span></p>\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed> <img src=\"../../../assets/images/album/images23.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p xss=removed>As the subject of Earth Science is very vast, it needs a lot of focus, practice and study if you wish to master it. As a result, teachers give lots of Earth Science assignments to check out the understanding levels of students. Earth Science assignments take great deal of time of students owing to which they find less time to focus on other subjects. To help with Earth Science assignments, we at <strong><span xss=removed>Course Work Solutions provide </span>Earth Science assignment help</strong><strong><span xss=removed> in a very professional manner</span></strong> to attain excellent grades. We have expert <strong>Earth Science assignment help</strong> tutors who can help you with complete solutions containing stepwise explanation of your Earth Science homework, assignments, projects and research papers.</p>\r\n<p xss=removed>Don’t get intimidated when you’re requested to complete lots of Earth Science assignments. Take it in an extremely positive note and think that it’s a great opportunity to get more knowledge in this subject. We at <strong><span xss=removed>Course Work Solutions </span></strong><span class=\"style11\"><span xss=removed>offer expert help on extensive range of </span></span><strong><span xss=removed>Earth Science</span></strong><span class=\"style11\"><span xss=removed> subjects like <strong xss=removed>Geography, Geomorphology, Climatology, Environmental Geography, Oceanology, Geophysics, Geology, Geotechnical studies,</strong> etc and all the topics covered in these subjects.</span></span></p>\r\n<p xss=removed>The solutions provided by our <strong>Earth Science assignment help</strong><strong><span xss=removed> experts </span></strong>are intended to create learning experience for students and not just to provide assignments. By taking good <strong xss=removed>earth science assignment help<