(200, 'SUB00197', 'Civil Engineering ', 'civil-engineering', '', 'images16.png', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>Civil Engineering assignment help</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Civil engineering is the professional engineering discipline, which deals with the designing, construction and preservation of the naturally built and physical environment, including works like bridges, buildings roads, canals, and dams. Civil engineering is one of the oldest engineering disciplines after the military engineering, and was defined to differentiate military engineering from non-military engineering. It’s traditionally broken into numerous sub-disciplines including geotechnical engineering, environmental engineering, structural engineering, urban or municipal engineering, transportation engineering, materials engineering, water resources engineering, coastal engineering, construction, and surveying engineering. Civil engineering occurs on all the levels: in public sector from the municipal to the federal level, and in private sector from the individual homeowners to the international companies. So, this makes civil engineering a bit difficult field to study. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Students agree that the Civil Engineering field is one among the hardest disciplines in Engineering, and have hard time dealing the educational stress and assignments deadlines.</span><span xss=removed> The problems that cause students to require civil engineering assignment help are many. From the legal side of building within any city, to calculation of proper measurements, to common planning of any new construction – it’s all pretty heavy and not everybody can deal with it with easiness</span><span xss=removed> Thankfully, Course Work Solutions is home to team of highly experi