(201, 'SUB00198', 'Electrical Engineering ', 'electrical-engineering', '', 'images_(1)2.jpg', '<p xss=removed><strong xss=removed>Electrical engineering assignment help</strong></p>\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed>Electrical engineering is the field of engineering, which usually deals with study and applications of electricity, electromagnetism, and electronics.<span class=\"apple-converted-space\"> </span>Electrical engineering is division of engineering that utilize the principle of electricity and electromagnetism to generate and send out electric power, and therefore allow for the developments of multitude of electronic and electrical devices, including cooling and heating systems, telecommunication system, traffic lights, hybrid vehicles, CAT scans, etc. This field first became identifiable occupation in late 19<sup>th</sup> century just after commercialization of electrical power supply and electric telegraph. It now covers an extensive range of subtopics like power, electronics, signal processing, telecommunications and control systems. However, lots of students agree that the Electrical Engineering branch is one amongst the hardest fields of Engineering, and they have a difficult time coping with academic stress and Electrical Engineering assignments deadlines.</span></p>\r\n<p xss=removed><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span xss=removed> <img src=\"../../assets/images/album/images22.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p xss=removed> </p>\r\n<p xss=removed>The topics which require students to get <strong xss=removed>electrical engineering assignment help</strong> are many and students simply can’t tackle themselves. As with all the engineering disciplines, this is intimately related to even more than one type of physics. It is the reason why some of the students who focus in any specific field at times are unable to deal with others. An excellent example would be the electrical engineering assignment that deals with history of this discipline. A