(220, 'SUB00215', 'Business Principles ', 'business-principles', '', 'download40.png', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>The <strong xss=removed>Business Principles</strong> course provides a survey of economic systems, forms of business ownership, and considerations for running a business. This subject teaches students various aspects of business, <strong xss=removed>management, and leadership functions</strong>; organizational considerations; and decision-making processes. Financial topics are introduced, including accounting, money and banking, and securities markets. Also included are discussions of business challenges in the legal and regulatory environment, business ethics, social responsibility, and <strong xss=removed>international business</strong>. Emphasized is the dynamic role of business in everyday life. Since, the subject can be tricky at time as well owing to its essentiality in Business studies, hence <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong> has introduced <strong xss=removed>online classes help</strong> for students. This online course, <strong xss=removed>Business Principles 1301</strong>, aims to simplify the subject for your understanding.<span xss=removed>  </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed> <img src=\"../../assets/images/album/a40.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>The online course developed by our experts include various topics such as <strong>Exploring Business and Economics, Ethics and Social Responsibility, Exploring Global Business, Forms of Business Ownership, Analyzing Small Business, The Management Process, Organizing a Business, Producing Goods and Services, Building Human Resources, Motivating Employees, Creating Effective Marketing, Creating and Pricing Product and Distributing and Promoting Products.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong><span xss=removed> </span></strong></p>\r\n<p cla