(221, 'SUB00216', 'Business Continuity Disaster Recovery Management and Tactics', 'business-continuity-disaster-recovery-management-and-tactics', '', 'download_(1)8.png', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong xss=removed>Manufacturers</strong> are vital to the continual growth of the U.S. economy, contributing more than $2 trillion to our gross domestic product each year and accounting for nine per cent of the total American workforce, according to the <strong xss=removed>National Association of Manufacturers</strong>. When a disaster strikes the manufacturing industry or its supply chain, it has the potential to send significant ripples through the entire country, while also putting individual companies at risk of going under.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><img src=\"../../assets/images/album/a41.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed>Manufacturers face several unique challenges when it comes to ensuring business continuity and effectively recovering from a crisis. Hence, <strong xss=removed>Business Continuity Disaster Recovery Management and Tactics</strong> is a subject that is important to be learnt and understood during the study. To ease the process of studying this crucial subject, <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong> has introduced <strong xss=removed>online classes help</strong>. The online classes for <strong xss=removed>Business Continuity Disaster Recovery Management and Tactics </strong>have been designed to make the subject easy to understand and focusses on its most important aspects. The online course is divided into 10 online classes. Only 2 classes occur in a week. Hence, this course is light so that the students can easily manage it along with their regular classes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed>The various topics covered under the online classes for <strong xss=removed>Business Continuity Disaster Recovery Management and Tactics</strong> are <strong xss=removed>BC/DR Concepts and Definitions, Business Impact Analysis, Human Resources (HR) Side of BC, Issues that Impact your Employees during and after a Disaster, Identification of Risks, Mitigation Strategies Evaluation, Recommendations to Management, Detailed Information on how to prepare, manage, complete and audit the following Recovery Plan Exercises, Establish Strategies for External/Internal Communications during Emergency, Establish and Document Program, Establish Crisis Communications Team with Appropriate Stakeholders Involved, Setting up the Command Center for Recovery and learning to conduct a Damage Assessment Review before a company declares a Disaster</strong>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed>The online classes help at <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong> has been designed by a panel of experts which is not only highly qualified but is also very experienced in their field of expertise. The classes have been designed in such a way that there is proper coverage of both theoretical as well as practical aspects. The classes are offered by us at a very low price as student welfare is our topmost priority. We even have a dedicated customer care team that is on its feet 24/7 to ensure consistent help and support. Get in touch with us if you wish to join <strong xss=removed>Business Continuity Disaster Recovery Management and Tactics online classes.</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed> </p>', 'COS0072', NULL, NULL),
(222, 'SUB00217', 'International Marketing 4143', 'international-marketing-4143', '', 'images17.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>International Marketing</span></strong><span xss=removed> is a topic that excites many students. This subject peeks into more than what you might really think. It goes on to explore all factors that influence marketing at International locations including political and legal scenario. An understanding of the purchasing power of individuals in a country is also essential for marketing at International locations as purchasing power can hugely influence <strong xss=removed>marketing strategy</strong>. We, at <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong>, realize the importance and potential of the subject. Hence, we wish to ensure that students in this field of study are well-versed with this subject and with exactly this motive, we have come up with <strong xss=removed>online classes help</strong> for <strong xss=removed>International Marketing</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><img src=\"../../assets/images/album/a42.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Our online classes for students cover a number of topics of International Marketing such as <strong xss=removed>Introduction to Global Marketing, The Global Economic Environment, The Global Trade Environment, Social and Cultural Environments, The Political, Legal, and Regulatory Environments, Global Information Systems and Market Research, Segmentation, Targeting, and Positioning, Brand and Product Decisions in Global Marketing, Pricing Decisions, Global Marketing Channels and Physical Distribution, Global Marketing Communications Decisions I: Advertising and Public Relations, Global Marketing, Communications Decisions II: Sales Promotion, Personal Selling, and Special Forms of Marketing Communication, Global Marketing and the Digital Revolution, Strategic Elements of Competitive Advantage and Leadership, Organization, and Corporate Social Responsibility.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>The <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions’ International Marketing 4143 is an online course</strong>, the objective of which is to </span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed>provide students with the understanding of important marketing issues in the context of a global business. Specifically, we will investigate strategies, policies, and various factors in making international marketing decisions, and learn how to <strong>apply </strong>marketing principles in an international business environment. The similarities and differences between ‘<strong xss=removed>domestic’ marketing and international marketing </strong>will be analyzed in terms of economic, cultural, social, political, and legal environments, as well as business strategies. In summary, students will <strong>obtain the knowledge and develop the skills to apply various marketing strategies</strong>—e.g., product development, distribution, pricing, and promotion—in a global environment. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>This course has been established by highly competent experts. They have designed it to make it more and more practical as well as interesting.<span xss=removed>  </span>The joining fees for this course as well as any other course at Course Work Solutions’ is extremely small. If you wish to join the classes for <strong xss=removed>International Marketing 4143</strong>, then you can contact our customer care team via phone call or an E-mail.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></p>', 'COS0072', NULL, NULL),
(223, 'SUB00218', 'Marketing Research 4243', 'marketing-research-4243', '', 'download31.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>Marketing Research</span></strong><span xss=removed> is a course that has been designed to prepare the student to be an informed, effective user of marketing research. The course provides an overview of research techniques available for collecting information to answer specific research questions. Therefore, the primary orientation of the course is managerial. The purpose of this course is to teach students to be able to define a research problem, develop a well-constructed hypothesis, recognize a well-constructed questionnaire and identify flaws in poorly constructed questionnaire and understand and be able to implement alternative sampling plans. This is a course of great importance and hence <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong> has come up with <strong xss=removed>online classes help</strong> for students. This online course has been designed by our expert panel.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Various topics covered under the online course are <strong xss=removed>The Role of Marketing Research</strong></span><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>, </span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>Data Mining Procedures and Knowledge Systems</span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>, </span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>The Marketing Research Process</span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>, </span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>The Human Side of Marketing Research: Organizational and Ethical Issues</span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>, </span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>Qualitative Research</span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>, </span></strong><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>Secondary Data Research in a Digital Age</span></strong>