(237, 'SUB00232', 'Performance management', 'performance-management', '', 'download_(1)15.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong xss=removed><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed>Performance management</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed> is a process by which managers and employees work together to plan, monitor and review an employee’s work objectives and overall contribution to the organization. More than just an annual performance review, <strong xss=removed>Performance Management</strong> is the continuous process of setting objectives, assessing progress and providing on-going coaching and feedback to ensure that employees are meeting their objectives and career goals. Performance, as a subject, hence is an important subject for the sheer fact that it is a skill required to be omnipresent and a sign of quality leader. <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong> is an education firm and we have come up with <strong xss=removed>online classes help</strong> for <strong xss=removed>Performance Management</strong> course. This is a course designed specifically to benefit the students of this subject in their graduation or post-graduation. These online classes can compensate for unimpressive teaching in your college or anything that just flies over your head or you just fail to grasp or understand.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed>The various topics covered in the online course for <strong xss=removed>Performance Management</strong> are <strong xss=removed>Performance Management and Reward Systems in Context, Performance Management Process, Performance Management and Strategic Planning, Defining Performance and Choosing a Measurement Approach, Measuring Results and Behaviours, Gathering Performance Information, Implementing a Performance Management System, Performance Management and Employee Development, Performance Management Skills, Reward Systems and Legal Issues and Managing Team Performan