(293, 'SUB00288', 'Engineering Design 1003', 'engineering-design-1003', '', 'download_(2)2.png', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong xss=removed><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed>The engineering design</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed> process is a series of steps that engineers follow to come up with a solution to a problem. Many times the solution involves designing a product (like a machine or computer code) that meets certain criteria and/or accomplishes a certain task. Engineering design subject in the engineering course explores the skill sets to make <strong xss=removed>engineering design</strong> and also facilitates practice for future applications. Engineering design as a subject focusses on all these aspects and addresses them to train future professionals. With an objective of helping students with this subject of utter importance, <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong> has introduced online classes help for students.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed><img src=\"../../assets/images/album/a6.png\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed>Various topics covered in this online course are <strong xss=removed>Engineering Design overview, Schematic capture and Simulation, DC Power Supply Options, Diode Bridge Rectifiers and Zener Diode, Regulator circuits, Switching Power Regulators, Control of a Switching Power Regulators, Schematic Transfer to PCB, Component Selection and Snubbers, Thermal Management and Magnetic design</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=removed>The classes and the course have been designed by our panel of experts. These experts at <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong> are highly experienced and are really well-qualified. They have designed the course after extensive research on the subject so that the course remains relatively simple to deal with an