(294, 'SUB00289', 'Engineering Computing 1 (038292)', 'engineering-computing-1-038292', '', 'download62.png', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>Computer engineering</span></strong><span xss=removed> is a discipline that integrates several fields of computer science and electronics engineering required to develop computer hardware and software. Computer engineers usually have training in electrical engineering, software design, and <strong xss=removed>hardware–software integration</strong> instead of only software engineering or electronic engineering. Computer engineers are involved in many hardware and software aspects of computing, from the design of individual <strong xss=removed>microcontrollers, microprocessors, personal computers, and supercomputers</strong>, to circuit design. This field of engineering not only focuses on how computer systems themselves work, but also how they integrate into the larger picture. This is a subject of great importance as mastery over it can make a successful career for you. <strong xss=removed>Course Work Solutions</strong> has, hence, introduced online classes help for students.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><img src=\"../../assets/images/album/download39.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Some of the various topics covered in this online course are <strong xss=removed>Introduction to Engineering Computing</strong></span><strong xss=removed><span xss=removed>, <span xss=removed>Data Types and Operators in C++</span>, <span xss=removed>Program Control Statements</span>, <span xss=removed>Introducing Functions</span>, <span xss=removed>Arrays, Strings and Pointers</span>, <span xss=removed>A Closer Look at Functions in C++</span> and <span xss=removed>More Data Types and C++ Operators</span></span></strong><span xss=removed>.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></p>\r\